[No. 7,298. In Bank.] PEOPLE v. J. S. McCUNE et al. Street Assessment—Jurisdiction—Legislative Power—Due Process of Law. Appeal from a judgment, in the Third District Court, City and County of San Francisco. McKee, J.

J. Luttrell Murphy, for Appellant.

D. H. Whittemore, for Respondents.

The Court:

Upon the authority of Brady v. King, 53 Cal. 44, and People v. Lynch, 51 id. 15, the judgment is affirmed.
